rows.label: qst500107_msg0001
rows.name: Hello-lo!

rows.label: qst500107_msg0002
rows.name:
Nonnon very busy excavating ruins,
so friends leave Nonnon alone!

rows.label: qst500107_msg0003
rows.name: What now?

rows.label: qst500107_msg0004
rows.name: Leave her alone

rows.label: qst500107_msg0005
rows.name: No no no, keep talking!

rows.label: qst500107_msg0006
rows.name:
Nonnon like it when people
do as Nonnon say.

rows.label: qst500107_msg0007
rows.name:
Nonnon say Nonnon very busy!
Why friends keep talking?!

rows.label: qst500107_msg0008
rows.name:
Nonnon need to excavate all ruins in
whole area and find Divine Beast weapons
like scary Aeshma!

rows.label: qst500107_msg0009
rows.name:
Probably take over 100 years to
excavate all ruins, so Nonnon can not
be wasting any moments!

rows.label: qst500107_msg0010
rows.name:
Now friends please leave
Nonnon alone to excavating!

rows.label: qst500107_msg0011
rows.name: Decisions, decisions...

rows.label: qst500107_msg0012
rows.name: Encourage her

rows.label: qst500107_msg0013
rows.name: No no no, Nonnon should stop

rows.label: qst500107_msg0014
rows.name: Thanks, friends, for support!

rows.label: qst500107_msg0015
rows.name:
Will make sure friends first to know
when Nonnon finish excavating!

rows.label: qst500107_msg0016
rows.name: No no no! Nobody stop Nonnon!

rows.label: qst500107_msg0017
rows.name:
Even Mamapon never stop Nonnon!
Even Brotherpon never stop Nonnon!
And strangers definitely can not-

rows.label: qst500107_msg0018
rows.name:
Wait...brotherpon?
Nonnon remember something about
brotherpon...

rows.label: qst500107_msg0019
rows.name:
Brotherpon...? Sisterpon...?
Twelve?

rows.label: qst500107_msg0020
rows.name: AHHHH!

rows.label: qst500107_msg0021
rows.name:
Nonnon not come here to Temperantia
for excavating! Come to find tasty-tasty
ingredients for juice!

rows.label: qst500107_msg0022
rows.name:
Nonnon work hard to make tasty
new juice for Twelve Brothersisterpon
drinks place in Avaritia!

rows.label: qst500107_msg0023
rows.name:
No, no, no... How could Nonnon get so
distracted by silly distracting ruins?

rows.label: qst500107_msg0024
rows.name: Nonnon is worst of all Brothersisterpon!

rows.label: qst500107_msg0025
rows.name:
No time to waste! Nonnon must find
Death Mushroom quick-quick and
take back to Avaritia!

rows.label: qst500107_msg0026
rows.name: Thanks friends for stopping Nonnon!
